Nitrogen fixation refers to the conversion of atmospheric
N<sub>2</sub> to ammonia and then to N containing organic compounds that can become
available to all forms of life.<br><br>\(\ce{N_2 + 16ATP + 8e^- +8H^+ \stackrel{nitrogenase}{\longrightarrow} 2NH3 + H2 +16ADP + 16Pi}\)&nbsp;

